  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Mechanical bowel preparation aims to decrease the volume fecal content in the colon, which
      thereby decreases the total colony count of bacteria, thus, decreasing peritoneal
      contamination in case of bowel injury, improving the access to the surgical field and
      facilitating intraoperative bowel manipulation
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
